snippet.title: PlayStation - Yuugen Kaisha Chikyuu Boueitai - Earth Defenders Corporation (1999) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Yuugen Kaisha Chikyuu Boueitai: Earth Defenders Corporation is a Strategy game, developed by Japan Art Media (JAM) and published by Media Rings, which was released in Japan in 1999.
